Package: nidaarem
Type: Package
Title: Damped Anderson Acceleration with Epsilon Monotonicity for Accelerating EM-Like Monotone Algorithms
Version: 0.1
Date: 2019-08-14
Authors@R: c(person("Nicholas", "Henderson", email = "nhender5@jhmi.edu", role = c("cre", "aut")), person("Ravi", "Varadhan", email = "ravi.varadhan@jhu.edu", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Nicholas Henderson <nchender@umich.edu>
Imports: stats, utils
Description: Implements the NIDAAREM method for accelerating the convergence of slow, monotone sequences from smooth, fixed-point iterations such as the EM algorithm. 
